modShortDescription: This mod reduces the damage of rockets and dynamite to blocks and increases the damage of the explosive arrows/bolts to entities.
modDescription:
A little tweaking on the explosive damage, reducing the damage of rockets and dynamite to blocks and increasing the damage of the explosive arrows/bolts to entities.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/Snufki-n/Snufkin_Modlets/tree/master/Snufkin_NerfExplosives)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/18673-snufkins-assorted-modlets/).
